property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT DISTINCT
    'CancelSalesOrderScheduleLine' || '::' || "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."ID"          AS "ID",
    "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."Time"                                          AS "Time",
    "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."ChangedBy"                                     AS "ExecutedBy",
    "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."ExecutionType"                                 AS "ExecutionType",
    "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."OldValue"                                      AS "OldValue",
    "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."NewValue"                                      AS "NewValue"
FROM "c_o_custom_SalesOrderScheduleLine" AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"        
WHERE "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."ID" IS NOT NULL  
    AND "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."Attribute" IN ('IsCanceled')
    AND "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
    AND "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."OldValue" = 'f'
    AND "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."NewValue" = 't'

sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 'CancelSalesOrderScheduleLine' || '::' || "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."ID"          AS "ID",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."ID"                                                    AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine"
FROM "o_custom_SalesOrderScheduleLine" AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine"
LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_SalesOrderScheduleLine" AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"
    ON "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."ID" = "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."ObjectID"
        AND "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."Attribute" IN ('IsCanceled')
WHERE "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."ID" IS NOT NULL
    AND"SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
    AND "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."OldValue" = 'f'
    AND "SalesOrderScheduleLine_Changes"."NewValue" = 't'
